{"tid":1350042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"EY：員工可採彈性工作安排","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:14:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"336db7f6fd4f5783fbf111f507bfd30d86c62871","tid":1350042,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"元朗昨晚發生嚴重暴力事件，網上今日流傳有不法分子或再在區內採取襲擊行動。<br />\n<br />\n安永發言人表示，一直以確保員工的安全為福祉，考慮到目前局部地區可能發生的混亂，建議今日將會經過或居住在元朗、屯門、天水圍及荃灣地區的員工提早下班回家，以保安全。<br />\n<br />\n該公司又建議，員工採取彈性工作安排，並遠離受影響地區，留在安全的地方。<br />\n<br />\n另外，外賣平台Uber Eats表示，為了保障外送員的人身安全，已於今日下午停止元朗區送賣服務。"},{"pid":"22c4d911d94ce27a997206f3e42bff9161e9f9fd","tid":1350042,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2197551/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2197551%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=b439976f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2197551/</a>"},{"pid":"335eb7e680e4d2f86fb2d037b3d8914686c455f3","tid":1350042,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1d7348cf1806f83e902d8a15ab38d94505dc75","tid":1350042,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:52:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2de1e05989c314fd468baa82ecb3cd95ecc9b428","tid":1350042,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"hoikilam <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df1ffbfffbda011ae4de4f748b98111114ab231","tid":1350042,"uid":123111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},